      OPTS="--bindir=/usr/games"
  ESTIMATE="111"
      DESC="crack-attack is a network multi-player variation of tetris.
crack-attack is a puzzle/action game in which you rush
to eliminate colored blocks before they fill your screen.
Particularly clever eliminations cause
garbage to clutter your opponent's screen.
Playable both online and off."

